| Type         | Use                       |
| ------------ | ------------------------- |
| `SERIAL`     | auto-increment integer ID |
| `TEXT`       | strings (default choice)  |
| `VARCHAR(n)` | length-limited strings    |
| `INTEGER`    | numbers                   |
| `NUMERIC`    | precise decimals          |
| `BOOLEAN`    | true/false                |
| `DATE`       | date only                 |
| `TIMESTAMP`  | date + time               |


